{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-371","title":"江河湖海","sectionId":"chapter-16","sectionTitle":"天文地理有规律","pageStart":1810,"pageEnd":1813,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":12,"duplicateEntryCount":20,"pages":[{"number":1810,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"371 江河湖海"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"rivulet [ˈrɪvjələt]","headword":"rivulet"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.小溪，小河"},{"type":"entry","text":"riverside [ˈrɪvəsaɪd]","headword":"riverside"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.河畔"},{"type":"entry","text":"The Great Lakes 五大湖","headword":"The Great Lakes"}]},{"number":1811,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"oceanic ridge 海岭","headword":"oceanic ridge"},{"type":"entry","text":"oceanic basin 海盆","headword":"oceanic basin"},{"type":"entry","text":"oceanic trench 海沟","headword":"oceanic trench"},{"type":"entry","text":"sea level 海平面","headword":"sea level"},{"type":"entry","text":"fretum [ˈfretəm]","headword":"fretum"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.海峡"},{"type":"entry","text":"coast guard海岸巡逻队队员","headword":"coast guard"}]},{"number":1812,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"main stream 主干流","headword":"main stream"}]},{"number":1813,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"shallows [ˈʃæləʊz]","headword":"shallows"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.浅滩"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"entry","text":"The Cape of Good Hope好望角","headword":"The Cape of Good Hope"},{"type":"text","text":"The Cape of Good Hope is located on Africa's southerly tip. Here, two"},{"type":"text","text":"oceans meet. One is the warm Indian Ocean, and the other is the chilly"},{"type":"text","text":"Atlantic Ocean.And as the two oceans mingle, they create a billowing cloak"},{"type":"text","text":"that drapes the summit of Table Mountain.Spectacular though this is, the"},{"type":"text","text":"mountain's cloudy covering is only a hint of the profound influence that"},{"type":"text","text":"these two very different oceans have on the fortunes of life here. And not"},{"type":"example","text":"just here at the Cape, but across the length and breadth of southern Africa."},{"type":"text","text":"好望角位于非洲的最南端。这里是两大洋交汇处，一个是温暖的"},{"type":"text","text":"印度洋，而另一个则是寒冷的大西洋。两大洋一相遇，就形成了密集"},{"type":"text","text":"的水汽云团，从而覆盖了桌山的山顶。尽管景色十分壮观，但山上缭"},{"type":"text","text":"绕的云雾只是那两大完全不同的海洋的相汇对此处生灵恩赐的一个缩"},{"type":"text","text":"影。不仅在好望角，整个非洲南部都受到了惠赐。"}]}]}